txt.en: You have been tasked with destroying the brigand blockade within the mines of Writhenset.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Radhril for your reward!

'Would you accompany me on a mission, [placeholder]?

'The Free Peoples in the Wildwood have reported a group of brigands who have barricaded themselves in the mines of Writhenset. It would seem these deviant Men have all but fled from the Wildwood.

'If the mines of Writhenset are to ever again be safe, this group of brigands must be removed.'

A group of brigands has locked themselves in the mines of Writhenset in a last ditch effort to control their foothold in the Wildwood.\n\nYour mission is to destroy the brigand blockade within the mines of Writhenset.
You must find a way to breach a barrier to reach your mission objective.
Your mission is to destroy the brigand blockade within the mines of Writhenset.\n\nSpeak to Radhril.

'We have done well, [placeholder]. With nowhere else to take refuge in the Wildwood, this group of brigands will certainly disperse. The mines of Writhenset will soon enough be safe for the Free Peoples, thanks to our efforts.'
